Class ObservablePatternMatcherRoot

    org.apache.log4j.Appender, org.apache.log4j.spi.OptionHandler

    public class ObservablePatternMatcherRoot
extends EngineTaintListener
    Each IEditingDomainProvider will be associated a PatternMatcherRoot element in the tree viewer. PatterMatcherRoots are indexed with a ViewerRootKey. It's children element will be PatterMatchers.
    Author:
    Tamas Szabo
